ji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:25:58.000Z","msg":"普通醫生 係順利邨 丁家柱醫生 真係好好既一個醫生   住屯門都特登去睇佢 $300有找 非打手 巴打都可以試下其他 如果真係越嚟越嚴重就即刻去急症室"},{"pid":"10083dc9b86286c3899edd4920fbb2a5a6849bb1","tid":2092432,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8731688d4da0b0d9fecb443040d9cbfd5f1cd914","tid":2092432,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:36:28.000Z","msg":"我有個方法<br />\n可以令佢唔再跳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:26:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb51d8ac5db0804bbfdd60d78a09fb24c609d0a3","tid":2092432,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:27:06.000Z","msg":"之前都係咁，跳快跳慢，屌佢老母 , 做番運動就無事"},{"pid":"845018053ef41a1aa16abbbae401a1cc8b6b2799","tid":2092432,"uid":185505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:28:05.000Z","msg":"有無手震腳震<br />\n食極都廋<br />\n可能係甲狀腺亢進"},{"pid":"7868479013a84a5d61b5f1480c4e15e2f0c6430d","tid":2092432,"uid":78434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"845018053ef41a1aa16abbbae401a1cc8b6b2799","tid":2092432,"uid":185505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:28:05.000Z","msg":"有無手震腳震<br />\n食極都廋<br />\n可能係甲狀腺亢進"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T17:01:18.000Z","msg":"屌係呀，我體型瘦呀，手偶爾搬完重野會keep住震一陣"},{"pid":"7b13760bdf172230770c47433e7a287f0649ede3","tid":2092432,"uid":151354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T17:06:22.000Z","msg":"之前試過有一排心跳keep住8x-9x<br />\n之後做番多少少運動，游下水<br />\n然後正常番變60幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62189fcf09ec079899d1076fcbedbfd1444107bf","tid":2092432,"uid":72991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"845018053ef41a1aa16abbbae401a1cc8b6b2799","tid":2092432,"uid":185505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:28:05.000Z","msg":"有無手震腳震<br />\n食極都廋<br />\n可能係甲狀腺亢進"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T01:27:11.000Z","msg":"去邊check好"},{"pid":"b5ebfb86c314723db38acb5b7f207a13ae6435b8","tid":2092432,"uid":319769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T01:34:12.000Z","msg":"我六月頭開始心悸、心跳快，頭暈眼花，發病時會有驚恐情況，有次就黎暈低入左急症，再係內科 check 過無問題，甲狀腺都正常。<br />\n<br />\n之後睇中醫，佢話好多人有類似病徵西醫又係 check 過晒咩事都無，其實係交感神經失調，係壓力引起。我食左中藥，有改善，不過佢講明係長期調理，起碼幾個月至一年。<br />\n<br />\n利申：每日都頭暈眼花，不過情況一日比一日好"}]}